      <title>GoTo 给 CEO 额外五年时间，让网约车公司实现盈利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/goto-gives-ceo-five-years-more-to-get-car-hailing-firm-to-profit</link>
